3 Load and transform data

# Loading the data
house_sale <- read.csv("/Users/sakshi/Documents/Syllabus/Data Visualization/Quick Project 1/qp1_data.csv")


# Transforming the data
house_sale$price_1000 <- house_sale$price/1000
house_sale$waterfront =as.factor(house_sale$waterfront)
house_sale$zip_code =as.factor(house_sale$zip_code)

mymode <- function(x) {
                 t <- table(x)
                 names(t)[ which.max(t) ]
           }
